{"tid":2027223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國安法其實唔可怕，我地應該立即轉換抗爭方式，名為加速主義行動","createTime":"2020-05-21T10:32:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T04:03:11.000Z","uid":98507,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"eebec09eae9c073d5393d8d6940109bb0ead93b7","tid":2027223,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:32:32.000Z","msg":"其實國安法我覺得係試水溫<br />\n係人權法報告出之前先下一著<br />\n睇下美國會點處理<br />\n如果美國唔理即係紙老虎 可以食得上<br />\n如果理就睇下理到邊一個地步<br />\n係試緊美國底線<br />\n不過無論美國點做<br />\n我地要做嘅只有一樣<br />\n就係轉變抗爭模式<br />\n而家嘅香港已經爛晒<br />\n一定要先毁滅一次<br />\n亦即係攬炒巴所講嘅死而復生 浴火重生<br />\n所以我地應該加速香港制度嘅滅亡，逼佢繼續強行立惡法<br />\n國安法，so what？<br />\n話明攬炒，你唔係覺得我地會驚下話？<br />\n夠薑就繼續黎"},{"pid":"5924ee18e414031e92a92b6c55c93de588e5d3aa","tid":2027223,"uid":73619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:33:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de6740768b2b7e2fc638346cf5657a547c96bd24","tid":2027223,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:34:08.000Z","msg":"加入現代義和團"},{"pid":"2b9d81915bad41f65709b03268b9d9090c7c4cca","tid":2027223,"uid":115847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:34:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fe39485c4fd5e7b3830575651e100283c962f4","tid":2027223,"uid":37303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896a0d9f5fa64563d46f140dead3f479b0d9d8e8","tid":2027223,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:35:07.000Z","msg":"加速主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces